				i'm of the 14 lvl mage and i think at lvl 8-12 you should go to black burrow which is very close to qeynos, and hunt giant snakes, the almost always drop snake fangs and drop venom sacks(use your earth pet for this) but if you like you don't have to come here till lvl 9 i hunted in gfay on the orc hill till 9 and with cb belts also hunted trainer hill but snakes in black burrow are much much much better and safer if you stay away from gnolls, and besides you have invis just invis yourself and walk to snake ledge.<BR>
<BR>
12-16 congratz on lvl 12 now go bye your lvl 12 spells(if you don't have much money yet i suggest you buy your fire pet and your new nukes and maybe burnout but you HAVE to buy bind and make sure you also have gate) now go to surefall glade many many druids here to give you a port unless one of them is in qeynos or qeynos hills and ask for a port to either fp or bb i went to fp but butcherblock works just as good if not better.  if you went to fp then hop the boat to bb and if you got a port to bb then go to docks. no matter how you got to bb bind yourself at the docks and hop back on the boat(if you came by the boat from fp you have to go quick) and once you zone go to the right side of the boat facing the front of the ship. once you see the rock with two alluring sirens and 2 aqua goblins JUMP, goblins are usually green to blue mostly light blue and always drop hunting bows which sell for 1 gold to a merchant and sometimes weapons and upon these weapons might be a bronze so kill the goblins but the exp is from the sirens. they are only lvl 12 so you and a white pet will take them np and they drop good money and save some mermaid scales for you'll need them for a focus item quest and just hunt here till lvl 16 once there go to ac island and buy spells from there (high elf merchant) don't worry it's almost always camped so not much to worry about.<BR>
<BR>
well i'll most likely add more to this but not as a comment i just wanted to make this guy mad =/.i wish you gl and happy hunting<BR>
